  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<h3 class=\"big-one-two\">獵豹PK小學中年級教學示範課程說明 楊譯老師</h3>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:22px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:22px;\">數學的學習，許多人都受限於：老師有沒有教過這題？是否學過這單元？是否見過這種題型？</span></strong></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fZCptDdLd0o?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">在獵豹小學PK的啟蒙學習，老師希望教導孩子的是：數學的思維方式！<br />\n而不在重複固定題型打轉，少有套路公式，避免填鴨知識！<br />\n著重在讓孩子跳脫章節單元限制，靈活思考，不斷燒腦！</span><br />\n<br />\n日前PK直播中，授課楊譯老師特地為大家示範一段教學，一開始的雞兔同籠問題，相信許多孩子都會說見過很多次了，但是，聽課並不是只聽老師解某一題就結束。<br />\n<br />\n好的學習是培養敏銳觀察和思考，沒見過的題目也能加以分析、思考、進而解決它、甚至發展它！<br />\n<br />\n影片中，老師利用雞兔同籠問題先帶孩子觀察和推論，到了第二題，是一題速度的題目，看起來和雞兔同籠並不相干，其實可以利用相同的思維模式解出！<br />\n<br />\n最後老師也帶給大家第一期PK課程中上課的畫面，孩子在豐富的課程進行中，除了提升數學能力，更是享受數學學習的樂趣！</span></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span></span></span><editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\"></editor-squiggler></p>\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n</editor-squiggler></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/951845379101481/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/951845379101481/</a></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\">&nbsp;</p>\n<editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n</editor-squiggler></div>\n<editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n</editor-squiggler></div>\n</div>",
